.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: emerald, ebony, purple, light-blue, lilac
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, dutch, french, turkish, indian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, 7up, sprite, iced-tea
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: emeraldmaster, tiparillo, oliveros, aristoff, havana
5 different pets are kept: lizard, chinchilla, rabbit, hedgehog, pony
1. the thai is the person who likes purple
2. the swedish is the owner of the rabbit
3. the dutch is the person drinking sprite
4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes light-blue
5. the person who likes ebony is the person drinking juice
6. the oliveros-smoker is the owner of the chinchilla
7. the person who likes lilac is the tiparillo-smoker
8. the person drinking 7up is in the middle
9. the turkish is on the far left
10. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard
11. the owner of the ponys is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker
12. the emeraldmaster-smoker is the person drinking mirinda
13. the french is the aristoff-smoker
14. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald
15. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    lilac	|     emerald	|      purple	|     ebony	|     light-blue	|
| Nationality	|   turkish	|    dutch	|    thai	|    french	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     lizard	|    pony	|     chinchilla	|     hedgehog	|      rabbit	|
| Beverage	|    iced-tea	|     sprite	|     7up	|    juice	|      mirinda	|
| Cigar		|   tiparillo	|    havana	|  oliveros	|    aristoff	|   emeraldmaster	|
